---
title: One-Pan Santa Fe Pork Tacos with Monterey Jack & Cilantro Lemon Slaw
description: We firmly believe taco night should be treated like a holiday—one that should be celebrated at LEAST once a week, if not more. If you agree, you’ve got to add this Southwest version to your repertoire. Spiced ground pork and onion are piled into steamy tortillas with Monterey Jack cheese, a tangy cilantro lemon slaw, and sour cream. Taco ’bout a killer meal.
